name: Camping & Hiking
description: Connect with Mother Nature by spending time outdoors hiking and camping. Hiking involves walking outdoors on a trail or path for recreational purposes. Hiking is a great form of exercise and can help revitalize your mind and body. People who work in stuffy offices and follow a sedentary lifestyle, must go hiking or camping in order to break free from their normal everyday routine. Camping involves staying overnight at the campsite either in a tent or a caravan. These campsites are normally far from cities and found in national or state parks. Hiking and camping can teach respect for nature, self confidence, teamwork and the ability to think on your feet. The equipment needed while camping have to be lightweight, compact, durable and most importantly useful during your trip. Hiking has many health benefits like improving your endurance and stamina from walking long distances.

name: Cycling
description: Cycling is a very efficient and cost effective way to travel short to medium distances without polluting the environment. Cycling is defined as the use of bicycle for sport, transport and recreation. With the number of cycles in the world crossing a billion, they have become a popular mode of transportation in many countries. There are many benefits to riding a cycle instead of using your motor car or bike. If you care about the environment and want to reduce your carbon footprint, riding a cycle is for you. A cycle does not burn fossil fuel to work and therefore does not create any air or noise pollution. You can avoid the traffic congestions on the road and cycle past them on the sidewalk to reach your destination quicker in cities. Cycles offer greater maneuverability and can be parked anywhere by chaining it to a fixed object.

name: Running
description: Running is an excellent way to get in shape without joining a gym and spending much money. You can run in a park, on a treadmill or simply around the block. Running can be quite invigorating and helps relax your mind. Depending on the weather, wear the appropriate clothes to enhance your running experience. Wear the right socks that help absorb moisture from your feet and ensure the shoes you use is also specifically designed for running. Slowly increase the distance you run over time to see better results. Running the same route everyday might get boring, so trying other routes will make it interesting. You can run alone by listening to your favorite music, or you can make it more fun by running with friends who also want to get fit. Encourage your running habits by rewarding yourself with running gear and equipment to make it even more fun to get in shape.

name: Squash
description: Squash is a fast paced indoor sport that is played between 2 players and involves hitting a small, hollow rubber ball in a four-walled court. You have to react very fast when playing squash as there is very little time in between your opponent hitting the ball and your turn. You have the option of playing a singles match with one other player or playing a doubles match with 2 players in each team. Squash is a descendant of the game called rackets from England and became popular in the twentieth century. You can play squash in clubs that have squash courts. There are various lines on a squash court that denote where you are supposed to serve from and where you can hit the ball. The bottom line on the front wall marks the out area and any ball hit below that line is out. The floor markings are only relevant during serving. Make your opponent work to hit the ball by smashing the ball to the extremes of the court.

name: Table Tennis
description: Many people all around the world play table tennis either for leisure or as a competitive sport. Also known as ping pong, table tennis is playable by people of all ages. Both men and women enjoy playing this action packed game. Table tennis is a low risk sport when it comes to injuries and the game can be taught to young children as it is a fun physical activity. Ping pong is played on a hard table with a low net dividing the table into two halves. There are different rules to serving and hitting the ping pong ball to the opponent's side of the table. Table tennis has been an official Olympic sport since 1988. This game is played with table tennis rackets and a hollow ball that bounces well on the hard surface. There are different ways of playing a shot and a skilled player can impart several varieties of spin to the ball altering its trajectory and thereby limiting his opponent's playing options. You have to have quick reactions to get to the ball quickly and smash it right back across the net.

name: Tennis
description: Tennis is a sport played all over the world and it is popular with people of all ages. This sport requires players to run and stretch in order to hit the ball back to their opponent's side of the court. The game starts with players serving the ball into the opponent's side followed by the opponent hitting it back. Whenever your opponent misses a shot, hits the ball outside the court or on the net, you get a point. Tennis is played by both men and women and there are several International level tournaments like the Wimbledon, French Open, Australian Open and US Open. Wimbledon first started in 1877 and is the oldest of the Grand Slam Tournaments played throughout the year. Tennis is played on different types of surfaces such as Clay, Hard, Grass, Carpet and Wood. Players like Rafael Nadal flourish on Clay courts while players like Roger Federer excel on Grass courts. There are different types of shots like the serve, forehand, backhand, volley, lob, overhead smash and drop shot.

The name Nivia was formed by combining the names of its founder Nihal Kharabanada and his son Vijay. This indigenous company was formed in 1934 and has expanded to include markets in Nepal and Bhutan. Nivia makes sporting goods and equipment for Football, Volleyball, Basketball, Cricket, Tennis, Hockey, Squash and Badminton. Nivia has supported Indian sportsmen and women in their struggle and earned nationwide legitimacy in every sport they participated in. Nivia is also taking the lead in popularizing games like Netball, Handball and Water Polo. They also focus on striving to create new innovations for popular sports to make it more enjoyable and empower the athletes to perform better. Nivia has also started making sport shoes for different sports like football, running, tennis, basketball and cricket.

Basketball is one of the most exciting team sports played with fast paced action and lots of scoring opportunities. Two teams of 5 players each compete against each other to score points by dribbling and shooting the ball through the opposite team's basket. If a player shoots a basket from inside the three-point line, he score 2 points, but if he scores from outside the three-point line, 3 points are added to the total score. Advance on the court by running or walking while dribbling the ball or pass the ball to your teammates in order to create scoring opportunities. There are specialized shots in basketball known as the lay-up, jump-shot, slam dunk, alley-oop, one-handed underhand shot and the hook shot. A free throw is awarded by a referee to a player who has been fouled by an opponent.

Cricket
description: Cricket is the most popular sport in India with millions of fans for the Indian Cricket Team. This game is played at different levels starting from school level tournaments all the way up to the international level tournaments. Sachin Tendulkar is India's most famous batsman and the inspiration for many a young batsman aspiring to touch the sky. Cricket is a game of skill and physical ability with players having to play for long hours depending on the game format. There are three main formats in cricket which are the limited overs 20Twenty format, limited 50 over one-day format and the unlimited overs Test format played over 5 days. Cricket originated in England and has become popular in countries like Pakistan, Sri Lanka, Australia, South Africa and West Indies.

name: Footboll
description: Football is an International game that is played all over the world and it is popular with people of all ages. Both men and women play this sport competitively with tournaments starting at the school level all the way up to the World Cup level. Football is an easy game to learn and it comes with many health benefits. Football helps improve your stamina and endurance as you have to run a lot during the game to maintain control of the ball. A football team consists of 11 players, playing in different positions such as forward strikers, midfielders, defenders and a goalkeeper. Only the goalkeeper is allowed to touch the ball with his hands, while all the other players are only allowed to kick the ball. The objective of the game is to kick the ball into the opposing team's goal post. Football requires dedication and practice to play as a team.

description: The Gate Valve is also known as a sluice valve. This type of valve opens by lifting a round or rectangular gate out of the path of the fluid. The sealing surfaces between the gate and seats are planar. This makes them an ideal choice when a straight-line flow of fluid and minimum restriction is desired.
name: Gate Valve

description:
Globe Valve is a type of valve consisting of a movable disk-type element and a stationary ring seat in a spherical body. This valve is generally used for regulating flow in a pipeline. Due to its salient features, globe valve is used for applications requiring throttling and frequent operation. 

We manufacture best quality globe valves in compliance with the international standards of quality. Following are the technical specifications for the globe valves offered by us.
name: Globe Valve
